Process Used to Verify an Access and/or Deletion Request
If you are a Dermstore customer, you will be required to verify your Dermstore account using your email address and password on the website or by contacting Customer Service at 1.800.213.3376 and providing 3 pieces of information associated with the account including your full name, address, and email address or phone number. Dermstore will use this information to search our systems and determine if we have information about you. If we are able to locate information about you, we will fulfill your Personal Information report and/or your Deletion request. If we are not able to match all 3 pieces of information you submit, we may provide you with a report that includes the categories of personal information we collect, use, disclose, and sell.
If you have a Dermstore.com account, your Personal Information report will be ready and viewable immediately on the website. You will need to be signed into your account to view your report. If you have contacted Customer Service to request your Personal Information report, we will mail your Personal Information report to the physical address you prefer on the account. You will receive an email with tracking information once the report is mailed.
If you are an Authorized Representative, you will be required to submit your name, address, email or phone number as well as the full name, address, email or phone number associated with the account of the Dermstore customer you are making a request on behalf of. Dermstore will use the customer’s information to search our systems and determine if we have information about the customer. If we are able to locate information about the customer we will fulfill the Personal Information and/or Deletion request. As an Authorized Representative, the Personal Information report will be sent to the physical address you have given us with a signature required upon delivery.
Dermstore will satisfy deletion requests through de-identification, which will be completed within 45 days from the date of the initial request. If additional time is needed, we will inform you.
Upon requesting that Dermstore delete your information, you will lose the following:
All outstanding Dermstore Rewards points
